public class WorldGraphRepositoryFolder extends com.telenav.kivakit.filesystem.Folder implements Serializable
A WorldGraphRepositoryFolder is a folder within a WorldGraphRepository that has a name based on the Metadata of the world graph information that it contains. The repository containing this folder can be retrieved with repository() or parent() and the WorldGraphIndex within the folder with indexFile(). A folder can be checked to determine if it is a valid world graph folder with check(Folder, Check).
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
